of what is going to come up in the future,

00:12:19.467 --> 00:12:21.636 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah is going to do the same thing.

00:12:21.636 --> 00:12:24.556 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Like the Scriptures say, we get our plagues.

00:12:24.556 --> 00:12:25.807 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We have those times.

00:12:25.807 --> 00:12:29.185 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But overall, when you’re in Jehovah’s arms,

00:12:29.185 --> 00:12:31.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
what’s the worry?

00:12:31.187 --> 00:12:33.398 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You could say that every one
of the Governing Body’s faith

00:12:33.398 --> 00:12:37.277 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
