00:12:41.156 --> 00:12:44.075 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And how Jehovah is directing us!

00:12:44.075 --> 00:12:46.244 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And he’s preparing his people

00:12:46.244 --> 00:12:48.371 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
