00:13:08.266 --> 00:13:11.561 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As a result, our trust
in Jehovah’s organization

00:13:11.561 --> 00:13:14.522 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is stronger than ever before.

00:13:14.522 --> 00:13:17.025 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And building this trust now is vital

00:13:17.025 --> 00:13:21.613 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
